title: Preview: Tech heads to Waco for series with Baylor - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Preview: Tech heads to Waco for series with Baylor - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: WACO, Texas – After a tough midweek road loss to Abilene Christian on Wednesday night, the Red Raiders look to bounce back in Waco as they face the Baylor Bears in a three-game series Friday, April 22 through Sunday, April 24 at Getterman Satdium.
